Name: BendSwanpPlanet
Notes: A special planet that can fold two times. Each state also has a separate collision mesh that gets loaded in. Usually, the planet will be in its unfolded state. SW_A and SW_B are used to fold it.

SW_A.Description: If activated, it will enter the first folding state.

SW_B.Description: If activated, it will enter the second folding state.
